.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, apricot, black, ivory
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, dancing, magic-tricks, skydiving
1. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who likes black##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1
4. the person who likes ivory is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is dancing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Color   | red        | black | ivory  | apricot |
| Hobby      | magic-tricks | dancing  | skydiving | card-games    |

