.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, gospel, house, punk
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, card-games, writing, puzzles
1. the fan of gospel is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
5. the fan of electronic is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the fan of house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | punk   | gospel | electronic | house      |
| Hobby     | writing | gardening    | card-games  | puzzles |

