.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, lacrosse, soccer, weightlifting
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, chaman, oliveros, prince
1. the davidoff-smoker is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the chaman-smoker is between the person who's sport is soccer and the oliveros-smoker##2
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
4. the davidoff-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | biathlon | weightlifting | soccer     | lacrosse   |
| Cigar   | oliveros   | chaman     | prince | davidoff |

