.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, garlic, peach, plum
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, card-games, reading, singing
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person eating plum##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person eating peach##1
3. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person eating garlic and the person who's hobby is singing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | plum   | peach      | garlic   | avocado  |
| Hobby   | singing | card-games | reading | drawing |

