.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, rock-climbing, singing, writing
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, freelancer, police-officer, lawyer
1. the police-officer is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the freelancer is on the left of the lawyer##1
3. the videographer is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is the freelancer##1
5. the videographer is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the freelancer is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is writing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | singing | writing | filmmaking |
| Job   | police-officer          | freelancer     | lawyer  | videographer     |

