.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-16::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, golf, climbing, swimming
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, scooter, subway
1. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is the person driving the scooter##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person driving the scooter and the person who's sport is golf##2
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
5. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |
| Sport   | badminton | golf | climbing | swimming |
| Transport     | bike     | bus   | subway | scooter  |

