.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-17::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, designer, mechanic, nurse
4 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, lizard, rabbit
1. the teacher is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the nurse is the owner of the lizard##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the goat and the designer##2
4. the owner of the rabbit is the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Job   | nurse | designer | teacher | mechanic |
| Pet           | lizard  | rabbit  | goldfish | goat      |

