.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, rabbit, fish, goldfish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, golf, rowing
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is between the owner of the ferret and the owner of the fish##2
5. the owner of the fish is the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Pet   | goldfish   | ferret   | rabbit | fish |
| Sport         | baseball | basketball | rowing     | golf    |

