.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, chestnut, blood-red, red
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes emerald is between the owner of the cat and the person who likes red##2
3. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
4. the person who likes chestnut is on the far right##1
5. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Color   | blood-red    | red     | emerald | chestnut |
| Pet     | chinchilla | guinea-pig | goat       | cat     |

 